{
  "title": "Pungent Algerian Beet Wrap",
  "description": "A pungent and indulgent Algerian dish featuring beets, blanched and wrapped in a low-carb lotus leaf wrap, perfect for a snack or light meal.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
  "diet": [
    "low-carb",
